settings.description:
Fly, slide and spin through the sky and Bowser's castle!
(For Smaghetti Build Contest #2.)
This is over world/fortress Bossfight where there are first world and fortress! The enemy is gombass, red koppa and the boss Boom Boom! Well that's it!
Mario got lost in the desert, meanwhile he finds several pipes that direct him to different places but he wants to cross the barrier once and for all.
Use the metal mushroom to get to the top of the temple, where you'll face off against Big Boo!
You sneak into Boom Boom's Japanese castle in Kyoto like an cool guy, and you have to defeat him!
This course includes the new SMB2 mushroom!
Embarking a Journey on the First Unused level but It's Improved by a little bit, Good luck finding the hidden Ace coins!
